entry.def: If you redouble your efforts, you try much harder to achieve something. If something redoubles, it increases in volume or intensity.

example.ex: The president also called on nations to redouble their efforts to negotiate an international trade agreement...
example.tran: 总统还呼吁各国就签订国际贸易协定加倍努力进行磋商。
